@AsaBertze You are correct, the voucher offer is not written in the fare rules so if it is withdrawn in the future it will not be possible to request a voucher then.

Kind regards,
Anton.

@AsaBertze Hello! The offer for free rebooking until 72h before departure is written in the ticket fare rules, if this offer is withdrawn in the future - all tickets booked while the offer was available will still have this security.

Kind regards,
Anton.

@FlyingDryden Hej! Inga SAS IT-system påverkades av dataintrånget.
Det finns inget behov av SAS EuroBonus-medlemmar att vidta några åtgärder i detta fall.

//Vänliga hälsningar, Dennis.

@AntonsenAre Vi beklagar att ni upplever det så, rapporten om skadad barnvagn måste skapas inom 7 dagar - efter detta är det dessvärre för sent.

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@AntonsenAre Hej! Vi beklagar att er barnvagn blev skadad. Om det var mindre än 7 dagar sedan barnvagnen blev skadad kan ni öppna ett claim med SAS Customer Care för vidare hjälp i ärendet https://t.co/ycN0llUB2g

Med vänlig hälsning,
Anton.

@SuperMo_ Hello! This error usually occurs when the ticket you are booking is displayed in a different currency than the currency your voucher is issued in. Please check if the currency of the ticket and the voucher matches.

Kind regards,
Anton.

@francesparry Hi. We can unfortunately not help with individual cases here on Twitter. Through our chat function you can chat with a chat agent that will help you take a look at what is possible for your voucher.

Kind regards,
Anton.

@GrumpyMathTeach Hello! Until further notice we offer free rebooking for all international trips up until 72 hours before the departure. You can read more about the free rebooking here: https://t.co/cKnrt7ebVN under "Free rebooking".

Kind regards,
Anton.

@francesparry Hello, thank you for contacting us! 
I would ask you to contact customer service and we will take a closer look at the rules that apply to your voucher. You can contact us via the contact information on this page: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj
Kind regards, Anja

@SuperMo_ Hello, Thank you for contacting us! 
The remaining amount will remain on the same voucher. You can check the balance and validity period here: https://t.co/ui2Ls6yWKm

Kind regards, Anja

@petros_cham We are sorry for the long handling time, however we are not able to help with specific bookings here on Twitter. You are welcome to contact us through Facebook Messenger or live-chat for more direct help regarding your refund request.

Kind regards,
Anton.

@petros_cham Hello. You can send us a message through Facebook Messenger or contact us on live-chat by following this link: https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards,
Anton.

@petros_cham Hello. We apologize for the delay in the handling time of refund requests, please contact us with your booking reference via Messenger and we will take a look at the current status of your refund request.

Kind regards,
Anton.

@DrBradMcKenna Hello! You can read more about EU passenger rights on our website here https://t.co/PYD5U9TLG8

Kind regards,
Anton.

@Esukki2 We don't require a test for the flight itself, however if the authorities in the country you are traveling to requires this we will check it prior to boarding. For more clarification on transit rules in Sweden we recommend that you contact the embassy.

Kind regards,
Anton

@Esukki2 Hello! We follow the entry restriction rules of the country are traveling to or through with transit. We only require a negative test when boarding if the authorities in the country you are traveling to requires us to check this.

Kind regards,
Anton.

@FlyersFfca Hello! We need to generate profit to be able to reinvest in our own business. In 2025 we plan to use 5-10% SAF and in 2030 around 20% - but probably more.

Kind regards,
Anton.

@mhunnibell Hi! 
You can contact us via Messenger or the chat if you have any questions about your Eurobonus, so i recommend that you contact us there if you can't call our Eurobonus department.

// Best regards, Dennis.

@mhunnibell Hello! If you need help with questions regarding Eurobonus you can also contact us on the live-chat. You can chat with us on our contact info page here https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards,
Anton.

@KenWakefield12 Hello! I am sorry to hear that you have not received a refund yet. Please contact us by chat or phone with your booking reference so we can take a look at your refund request. Our contact information can be found here https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards,
Anton.

@fabryprn Hello! We're sorry if you did not receive your refund yet. Please contact us by live-chat or phone with your booking reference and we will take a look at the status of your refund request. Our contact information can be found here https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards,
Anton.

@eriksigblad Hello! Please contact us on our live-chat or by phone with your booking reference and we will help you take a look at what alternatives there are for your voucher. Our contact information can be found here https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards,
Anton.

@Doyeen_Simbiat Hello! If the changes are not optimal for you please contact us by phone so we can help you look for other alternatives and rebook to a new flight. You can find our phone number list here https://t.co/b3QIqPk7bj

Kind regards,
Anton.
